{"tid":2012910,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭：積極向大聯盟提供支援 凌駕區議會地區工作","createTime":"2020-05-12T03:29:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T15:18:48.000Z","uid":21470,"like":5,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1afb9cb32959d6d4f92080c71a9e0f4b8ab03b52","tid":2012910,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:29:29.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥冀「再出發大聯盟」協助呼籲業主減租<br />\n12.05.2020 11:02<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥出席行政會議前表示，期望剛成立的「香港再出發大聯盟」，協助呼籲大小商鋪業主減租，指自己過去曾多次呼籲，但成效不彰，認為業主應該與商戶共渡時艱。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥指，她同意大聯盟發表的共同宣言，指本港面對嚴峻局面，不能夠再這樣下去，不論在改善民生、重視法治等方面，都要重新出發。她又指，大聯盟成立之前，她有與牽頭的全國政協副主席、前特首董建華和梁振英，以及全國人大常委譚耀宗見面，指政府不會參與大聯盟的工作，應該由民間主導，但如有需要，當局會提供支援。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1286950&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1286950%26csid%3D261_341&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HZq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=7c27be20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1286950&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"64d6c9ad1bb66d21204696922a0d2b584c30b5f2","tid":2012910,"uid":53498,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:30:15.000Z","msg":"黑社會屈人減租"},{"pid":"26b4c236f505c580707319490faab4c8ce734de6","tid":2012910,"uid":8014,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:33:06.000Z","msg":"你嗰堆乜柒發起人咪坐擁左香港9成私人物業資產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己呼籲自己減租？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5e3fb012d15a82af7a1a5eb712b9516c0ed118","tid":2012910,"uid":47355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:33:12.000Z","msg":"架空區議會去派餅"},{"pid":"942fa03804d2b5b09ba46f0567736015118bf416","tid":2012910,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64d6c9ad1bb66d21204696922a0d2b584c30b5f2","tid":2012910,"uid":5